se it increases the business‚Äôs "},{"_key":"e9e7fbf1a834","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"productivity and competitiveness"},{"_key":"5085b0d10270","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" (which is another way, is also a reward for investors)."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"12c17b897368","_type":"link","href":"https://finance.yahoo.com/"}],"style":"normal"}],"comments":[],"description":"A \"reward\" to shareholders.","mainImage":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-790b45f35e7a7fdfc92ed22174d292230701d894-750x500-webp","_type":"reference"}},"slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"dividend"},"title":"Dividend"}},"__N_SSG":true}